data.title: Music Rough Guides
data.text:
Founded in 1994, the Rough Guide series is produced by World Music Network in association with Rough Guide books and delivers the best possible starting point for exploring different music from all over the world.

Design evoltuion:

- From RGNET 1145 back cover changed with all credits placed at bottom instead of right frame

- New design with orange logo on front cover appears around end of 2005 / 2006
